<p><a href="/wiki/Cardiomyopathy" title="Cardiomyopathy">Cardiomyopathy</a>: <a href="/wiki/Dilated_cardiomyopathy" title="Dilated cardiomyopathy">Dilated</a> (<a href="/wiki/Alcoholic_cardiomyopathy" title="Alcoholic cardiomyopathy">Alcoholic</a>)<span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Hypertrophic_cardiomyopathy" title="Hypertrophic cardiomyopathy">Hypertrophic</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Restrictive_cardiomyopathy" title="Restrictive cardiomyopathy">Restrictive</a> (<a href="/wiki/Loeffler_endocarditis" title="Loeffler endocarditis">Loeffler endocarditis</a>, <a href="/wiki/Cardiac_amyloidosis" title="Cardiac amyloidosis">Cardiac amyloidosis</a>, <a href="/wiki/Endocardial_fibroelastosis" title="Endocardial fibroelastosis">Endocardial fibroelastosis</a>)</p>
